name: Vessels 164: WEASLE
description: Born with far-below-average intelligence, Weasle wears a cybernetic helmet that enhances his cognitive abilities up to just-below-average intelligence. Weasle, however, believes that he is far more intelligent that everyone else, and insists on being the one to come up with the plants (which is what he mistakenly calls the plans). Weasle is also a big believer in the conspiracy theory that the colony is not on another planet at all, but in fact simply on the underside of a flat Earth, and he has a theory that if everyone goes to one side of the disc and jumps in the air at once, when they land the whole thing will flip over. While he’s not sure what that would achieve, exactly, he theorises that it would be ‘pretty cool’ and that it ‘couldn’t make things any worse’.
